1
00:00:54,159 --> 00:00:55,479
Jiang Yue,

2
00:00:57,799 --> 00:00:59,320
Vice President of 3Z Group,

3
00:01:01,479 --> 00:01:02,799
Jiang Changfa's delivery man,

4
00:01:04,799 --> 00:01:06,120
I'm really looking forward to

5
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:08,040
how you're going to deal with

6
00:01:09,439 --> 00:01:11,959
the chess game I've prepared for you.

7
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,719
Hiding here, huh?

8
00:01:34,799 --> 00:01:36,400
What are you waiting for? Go!

9
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:57,159
You're looking for death!

10
00:01:59,959 --> 00:02:01,239
I'll kill you!

11
00:02:38,479 --> 00:02:39,039
Are you okay?

12
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:40,919
Don't bother.

13
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,400
Retreat, go.

14
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,080
This matter

15
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,840
should have been dealt with long ago.

16
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:50,919
It's my fault.

17
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,080
I apologize to you.

18
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:57,800
Let's go, I'll take you to fix the camera.

19
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:01,280
Let's go.

20
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,840
Don't bother.

21
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,400
You go.

22
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,840
This job was arranged by my father.

23
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,560
Do you think I'm happy to be a bodyguard?

24
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,919
Then he's the one who's meddlesome.

25
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,400
We are family now.

26
00:03:13,599 --> 00:03:14,199
Family?

27
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,120
What kind of family are we?

28
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,120
Jiang Yue, I never considered you

29
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,639
and your father as my family.

30
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,719
Before you came,

31
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:21,719
I was doing just fine.

32
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,719
And if you hadn't intervened,

33
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:25,120
no one would have interfered with my life.

34
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,319
I would have been better than now.

35
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,360
Don't follow me anymore.

36
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,719
I also want to go home.

37
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,400
Qi,

38
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,400
what's wrong with you?

39
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,439
Are you hurt again?

40
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,479
It's nothing. I just fell on the road.

41
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,080
I told you

42
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,039
to let Jiang Yue drive you,

43
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:49,599
But you insisted on walking to school.

44
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,479
Now you've made yourself look so miserable.

45
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:52,439
Are you worried about me,

46
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:53,520
or worried that his new daughter

47
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,319
won't be under his control?

48
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:55,520
Qi,

49
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:56,759
don't worry.

50
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,759
I won't let him lose face.

51
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,599
I won't mention him to anyone.

52
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,199
Because he'll never be my dad.

53
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,080
Qi Qi,

54
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,680
I bought you a new camera.

55
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,639
Don't use the old one all the time.

56
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,319
This is the first camera my dad gave me.

57
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:11,400
Don't you know?

58
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,720
Yue'er,

59
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,399
Changfa asked you to take care of Qi Qi.

60
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,199
I'm sorry to bother you.

61
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,040
Never mind.

62
00:04:59,079 --> 00:05:01,199
Dad, I want to take a picture of that.

63
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:01,839
OK.

64
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:15,759
Daddy, did I take a good picture?

65
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,199
Baby,

66
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:19,040
you will become

67
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,680
a hundred times,

68
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,000
a thousand times better photographer than me.

69
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:28,040
Daddy, I'm going to be six years old soon.

70
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:31,800
But I don't want to grow up.

71
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,160
Why?

72
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,000
When I grow up,

73
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,319
you will get old.

74
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:39,800
When you get old, you will leave me.

75
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:43,240
Dad, can you never leave me?

76
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,519
Okay.

77
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,040
I won't leave you.

78
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:23,680
Who is it?

79
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,439
It's me.

80
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,240
Open the door.

81
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,639
This CCD is already over a decade old.

82
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,240
Many of its parts are no longer produced.

83
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,079
Then,

84
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,680
do you have any other way?

85
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:54,399
Then you should tell me first

86
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:55,319
what's wrong with it.

87
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:57,160
It's this one.

88
00:06:57,839 --> 00:06:58,480
This one is broken.

89
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:11,680
Help me find this camera accessory.

90
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:21,920
I found it.

91
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:23,319
In a watch shop in Luocheng.

92
00:07:23,839 --> 00:07:24,399
Send me the location.

93
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,240
Young Master, it's so late.

94
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,279
It's over 300 kilometers away.

95
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:40,240
You're still up?

96
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,600
Why did you come back so late?

97
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,519
Parts.

98
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:55,399
Where did you find them?

99
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:59,040
What happened to you?

100
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,079
How did you get hurt?

101
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:01,839
Don't move.

102
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:02,680
It hurts.

103
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:34,960
You...

104
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,440
Why are you willing to help me?

105
00:08:40,399 --> 00:08:42,120
Because I know this is very precious to you.

106
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:48,919
My mother left it to me when she died.

107
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:49,960
Does it look good?

108
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,039
It's really beautiful.

109
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:06,639
Then do it for your mom.

110
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,679
Don't get hurt anymore.

111
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:15,440
I've taken care of it at school for you.

112
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,279
No need.

113
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,360
I figured it out when my dad died.

114
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,080
There's no need

115
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:28,720
to waste time on useless people and things.

116
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:32,919
But

117
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,080
thank you

118
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:41,879
for making me feel important.

119
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,240
Will you come to the opening of the art exhibition

120
00:09:49,039 --> 00:09:49,720
in a few days?

121
00:09:50,759 --> 00:09:51,480
What exhibition?

122
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:52,960
3Z

123
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,000
Okay.

124
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,480
Jiang Yue

125
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,840
This is the first big gift

126
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,159
I prepared for you.
